author: KIRO 7 STAFF
title: 1 killed after car collides with semi in Tacoma
text:
One person is dead after a crash involving a car and a semi in Tacoma.
Traffic detours were in place as the collision was investigated at East Portland Avenue and Puyallup Avenue.
Two people were in the car that collided with a semi.
Another person was sent to the hospital in critical condition.
One occupant transported from the scene in critical condition, and one deceased. Traffic detours in place. pic.twitter.com/x7Rfdvv1Hg
